					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“Don’t be ridiculous. It’s okay to cry when you’re sad. It’s okay to feel depressed when something bad happens.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“⋯⋯没这回事。悲伤的时候就好好哭。难受的时候就该好好沮丧。”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "禮"},
					"「⋯⋯沒這回事。悲傷的時候就好好哭。難受的時候就該好好沮喪。」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0028_00044",
		linknext = "0028_00046",
		line = 531,
	},
	["0028_00046"] = {
