					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“Now she’s forgotten all that awful stuff. She’s back to how she was when I was little. Friendly... loving...”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“虽然忘了很多的事。但以前⋯⋯在我还很小的时候，她对我很好。”",
