					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"I was about to argue, but thinking about it, it seemed obvious that she was right.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"我在一瞬间想质疑这点，但又稍稍想了想，我接受了这种说法。",
